          'To protect our rights, safety or the safety of others including for fraud prevention.',
        use_information_item_ten:
          'For any purpose required by law or regulation.',
        information_share_desc:
          'We may share your information with any of the following:',
        information_share_item_one: 'Our group companies.',
        information_share_item_two:
          'Carefully selected third parties with whom we have a relationship and who may contact you or utilise your data only for reasons pre-agreed with us, including marketing.',
        information_share_item_three:
          'Service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as: payment processing, information technology, Website maintenance, surveys and market research, warehousing and logistics, couriers, advertising and marketing or any service required.',
        information_share_item_four:
          'Our professional services providers such as: legal, audit, financial and insurance advisers.',
